Candelario

Candelario is a city in Salamanca, in Spain.

GPS Coordinates of Candelario, Salamanca, Spain

Candelario is located on the latitude of 40.36806 and longitude of -5.74499 and has a geohash of ez5vtkb8upbc.

Cities and Towns near Candelario

The nearest significant population center from Candelario is San Bartolomé de Béjar in Ávila, Spain, located 8 kilometers or 5 miles ↗ NE of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Becedas (Ávila, Spain) located 10 km (6 mi) ↗ NE and Neila de San Miguel (Ávila, Spain) located 10 km (6 mi) ↗ NE of Candelario.
